songs.title: Animal Kingdom

Crazy how the earth makes uh everything flat how the world is flat water doesn't fall like trees, trees are big yeah. So true ay fucking hell
Yeah like fields i don't know how they get big Do you know? uh i reckon Australia should be round and that's the final conclusion of the life
